                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Do you offer dental implants?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! Our dentists are leading implant specialists, providing both single-tooth and full-arch dental implants using robot-guided technology for precision and comfort.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I straighten my teeth without braces?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely. We help patients achieve beautifully aligned smiles with clear, comfortable aligners. Schedule a consultation to see if Invisalign treatment is right for you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What if I don't have dental insurance?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No problem! Our dental savings plan makes it easy to receive high-quality care without the stress of deductibles or waiting periods. Enjoy discounts on routine cleanings, fillings, and even cosmetic procedures.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I get a crown or filling in one visit?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes. With advanced CEREC and laser technology, we offer same-day crowns and no-shot fillings. That means fewer appointments and a more comfortable experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Do you treat TMJ pain and jaw discomfort?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes. Our TMJ treatment options include oral appliances, bite adjustments, and therapeutic treatments to reduce muscle tension and restore comfort.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
